CImg is C/C++ library for work with images. This example shows how compile and work with this library on android. CImg can use some external library. In example, we add libjpg and libpng.

P.S For build libjpg and libpng you can see:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12260149/libjpeg-turbo-for-android
https://github.com/julienr/libpng-android
